    "noValidateReason": "The string scalar form is documented in displaying_images.md. The object form {src, type} was added in v1.44.0 (changelog confirmed) and is implemented in element.js, but is not yet reflected in the markdown docs. Both forms are fully validated — this field is retained for transparency.",
